Designation of the female 
<typeStatus box="[639,723,942,963]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="BRULLE" authorityYear="1846" box="[756,949,942,963]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" genus="Myosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fasciatum">
<emphasis box="[756,949,942,963]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Myosoma fasciatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
– (First label, printed) “Museum Paris / EY0000001663”; (second label) “Museum Paris” (printed) “ 
<collectingCountry box="[970,1053,971,992]" name="Suriname" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Surinam</collectingCountry>
/ Leschenault” (handwriting); (third label, handwriting) “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Br" authorityName="Br" authorityYear="1846" box="[657,865,1000,1021]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" genus="Myosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fasciata">Myosoma fasciata Br</taxonomicName>
